# Project Conventions

## Environment
- Python 3.11, PyTorch 2.9.1, CUDA 13.0, RTX 5090
- Conda env: `emdiffuse`, activate with `source ~/miniconda3/bin/activate emdiffuse`
- Use `/home/djx/miniconda3/envs/emdiffuse/bin/python` for direct execution

## Data Paths
- Point cloud source: `/data0/djx/img2pc_2d/microtubules/`
- Generated images & training data: `/data0/djx/EMDiffuse/`
- Experiments/checkpoints: `/data0/djx/EMDiffuse/experiments/`
- Code repo: `/home/djx/repos/EMDiffuse/`

## Key Constraints
- Diffusion must operate in **real image space** (no latent space / VAE)
- All file output text in **English** (avoid Chinese encoding issues in plots/logs)
- User communication in **Chinese**
- Image size: 1024×1024, pixel size: 25 nm/pixel
- Density maps: normalized [0, 1], saved as 16-bit TIFF
- Training patches: 256×256, cropped from full images
